<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>RAL MI NAI ZOH TUAH U CH295</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ral an nai zoh tuah! ngiatnak puan hler u! Sualnak raldohnak Pathian
 ca, Nan hriam tim tuah u, dir thiu-theo ko u, Pathian Bia chungah nan zia
 bunh tuah.

[C1]
   Tho tuah, Khrihfa, ngiatnak puan dum tuah u, Timh cia ralring in
   Khrihfa au u, Hmai ah fong u, Ho-sa-na, tiah au u, Khrihfabu Ralbawi
   Jesuh a si.

[V2]
 Ral he ton duh ah, hmai ah fong chin u, Kannih nih kan tei lai kan
 hngalh, Kan ral dohnak kha Jesuh ca a tha, Bia tha caah kan taang bal lai
 lo.

[C2]
   Tho tuah, Khrihfa, ngiatnak puan dum tuah u, Timh cia ralring in
   Khrihfa au u, Hmai ah fong u, Ho-sa-na, tiah au u, Khrihfabu Ralbawi
   Jesuh a si.

[V3]
 Vancung um kan Pa, run kan ngai ko tuah, Pathian na vel in run kan
 bawm, Ral a dih tik le, kan tei hna tikah, Na teinak lu chin kan i chinh
 lai.

[C3]
   Tho tuah, Khrihfa, ngiatnak puan dum tuah u, Timh cia ralring in
   Khrihfa au u, Hmai ah fong u, Ho-sa-na, tiah au u, Khrihfabu Ralbawi
   Jesuh a si.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<hymn_number>295</hymn_number>
</song>